data.description: Motivated Seller **Price Improvement** Lowest priced WATERFRONT POOL HOME in Shore Acres - Must See!  Indulge in the ultimate waterfront living experience with this well maintained and enchanting 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom concrete block home, nestled on a serene cul-de-sac street in the highly sought-after Shore Acres neighborhood. From the moment you arrive, you'll be captivated by the lush landscaping, adorned with a delightful mango tree, leading to the welcoming front walkway and covered porch.  Step inside, and be greeted by an open floor plan that effortlessly blends indoor and outdoor living. Your eyes will be drawn to the birdcaged swimming pool, creating a focal point that perfectly frames the captivating open water views. This home is an entertainer's dream, with a spacious living room at its heart, seamlessly flowing into the large dining area boasting extended sliders that provide uninterrupted vistas of the tranquil waters. Privacy and comfort abound in this well-designed layout, as the three bedrooms are thoughtfully situated across the house. Each bedroom enjoys its own dedicated bathroom, two of which are private ensuite, ensuring the utmost convenience for all residents and guests. The primary bedroom is a true sanctuary, offering a generously sized walk-in closet, private bathroom with shower/tub combo, a private office or lounge space, and breathtaking water views through a poolside sliding glass door. Embrace the coastal lifestyle with ease, as the interior boasts tile and wood flooring, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of storage. The updates continue with the peace of mind provided by a shingle roof, newer soffits, facia, and insulation, as well as updated windows and sliders. Your comfort is further enhanced with a newer A/C and ductwork, ensuring your home remains a haven in every season.  Step outside to your backyard oasis, where entertaining is effortless with a full outside bar and seating area, covered poolside space with plenty of room for sunning, outdoor kitchen, built-in stainless steel grill, and a delightful tiki hut with tropical landscaping. Enjoy direct access to the water with your very own dock and electric boat lift, perfect for exploring the open water at your leisure. The expansive green grass area provides ample space for outdoor activities, complemented by delightful, lime, orange, grapefruit, plantain, banana, mango, and coconut palm trees. Additional features include an inside laundry room off the kitchen, a convenient one-car garage, a storage shed for all your tools, and a workout pad on the side of the house, catering to your active lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this waterfront paradise your forever home! Contact us today to schedule a private tour of 1625 Massachusetts Ave NE, St. Petersburg, FL 33703, and discover the epitome of waterfront living! This is a rare opportunity for a veteran to assume a mortgage of 2.25%. Buy with Roam and save monthly.
